(very easy to understand technic : send earth pet, he roots mob, back him off. resend pet to rerroot. nothing else to understand. Now the problem is to do that without being killed by mob breaking root : train into a zone where you can run out easily) <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Very unreliable. <br>
Earth often doens't get root off, and only can use against very limited mobs at 65. <br>
<br>
I.e. hard to use against golems in PoV, they have proc that tend to proc at the worse time. <br>
<br>
Also, earth pet seemed to have a hard time rooting them. <br>
