<br>
Bottom line:  If you want to do yo-yo rooting, always debuff with the malosi line of spells.  Makes all the difference in the world. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=balanzsonofanz>Balanz son of Anz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Abuser of EZCodes</span><br>  Posts: 3002<br> <font color=#333333>(2/27/03 3:42:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=570.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Battle tactics</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Yo-yo rooting works great for me using my 57 earth pet.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Yeppers.<br>
